  <summary date="2020-12-14T16:06:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Workforce Recovery and Training Services Act of 2020 

This bill establishes a grant program for states to provide employment training services to adults and dislocated workers. Of these funds, a specified amount must be allocated to areas most significantly impacted by the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</summary>
